data.description: Welcome home! This charming 3-bedroom/ 2.5 bathroom townhome is located in the highly sought after community of Parkview at Lakeshore. This home boasts an open floor plan a large eat in kitchen and separate dining room. The spacious living room leads you into the fenced in backyard oasis. The large detached 2-car garage is located in the back of the home. This community features a fitness facility, fishing pier, cabana, playgrounds, tennis court, sand volleyball court, nature parks and clubhouse. Conveniently located just minutes away from schools, shopping, theme parks and so much more.
